#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:46
msgid ""
"Image above (left) shows that when multiple objects are selected, the "
"pivot point is calculated based on the bounding box of all the selected "
"objects. More precisely, the centers of objects are taken into account."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:52
